    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2003 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather. This example features the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS variable valve timing. The powertrain is mated to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable differential lock. Mechanically flawless, the rod bearing recall has been addressed with documented shells, and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced to ensure structural rigidity. The suspension remains tight with refreshed bushings and factory-spec dampers, maintaining the communicative chassis dynamics this platform is known for. The exterior retains its factory depth with zero evidence of paint correction or panel misalignment, and the undercarriage is free of oxidation. This is a turn-key enthusiast piece with a comprehensive service dossier.",
      "price": 46500.0,
