    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This is an exceptional example of automotive preservation. Finished in a deep, lustrous metallic paint that has been professionally ceramic coated, the exterior is entirely free of rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks. It has been strictly garage-kept under a breathable cover and has never seen rain, let alone snow. Inside, the cabin retains its original factory scent; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, and the carpets have been protected by heavy-duty mats since day one. Every electronic feature, from the adaptive cruise control to the premium surround-sound system, functions with precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by certified technicians using OEM parts. The engine bay is meticulously detailed, and the undercarriage remains spotless. This vehicle is for the discerning buyer who demands a showroom-fresh experience without the new-car depreciation. It is, quite simply, as close to factory-perfect as a pre-owned vehicle can be.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
